query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `oauthSettings` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL,
  `provider` varchar(64) NOT NULL UNIQUE,
  `clientId` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `clientSecret` text NOT NULL,
  `tenantId` varchar(255),
  `redirectUri` varchar(500) NOT NULL,
  `scopes` text NOT NULL,
  `isActive` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 1,
  `createdAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `updatedAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  CONSTRAINT `oauthSettings_id` PRIMARY KEY(`id`)
);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `oauthProviders` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL,
  `userId` int NOT NULL,
  `provider` varchar(64) NOT NULL,
  `providerUserId` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `accessToken` text,
  `refreshToken` text,
  `tokenExpiresAt` timestamp,
  `profileData` text,
  `createdAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `updatedAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  CONSTRAINT `oauthProviders_id` PRIMARY KEY(`id`)
);
